00:27:28,647 --> 00:27:33,818
♪ <i>Stop me now</i>
<i>Don't stop me</i> ♪

453
00:27:33,902 --> 00:27:36,821
♪ <i>'Cause we're having a good time</i>
<i>Having a good time</i> ♪

